    <node id="interactionsE/414">
      <data key="d0">&lt;a href="javascript:alert(αS fibrils as interactor, Aβ fibrils as interactee. The authors focused on studying inhibition, not accelerated aggregation. Therefore, they do not conclude that accelerated aggregation occurred as a result of the interaction of αS fibrils and Aβ fibrils. I can see this on the ThT charts. The authors also investigate the effect of αS monomers / αS oligomers on Aβ fibrils. However, as  the authors' interpretation is not clear and it is difficult to read the kinetics from the ThT plots, I did not enter these interactions into the questionnaire.)"&gt;αS fibrils as interactor, Aβ fibrils as interactee. The authors focused on studying inhibition, not accelerated aggregation. Therefore, they do not conclude that accelerated aggregation occurred as a result of the interaction of αS fibrils and Aβ fibrils. I can see this on the ThT charts. The authors also investigate the effect of αS monomers / αS oligomers on Aβ fibrils. However, as  the authors' interpretation is not clear and it is difficult to read the kinetics from the ThT plots, I did not enter these interactions into the questionnaire.&lt;/a&gt;</data>
      <data key="d1">int:414(NI)</data>
      <data key="d2">2</data>
      <data key="d3">triangle</data>
      <data key="d4">#0bd11f</data>
      <data key="d5">10</data>
    </node>
